xmlGlossaryData += '                <div class=\"GlossaryPageDefinition\" id=\"MCDropDownBody_855183615_70\" style=\"display: none;\">Direct or indirect immediate consequences of fire. Examples of first order fire effects are biomass consumption, crown scorch, bole damage, tree mortality, soil heating, and smoke production. See also IFT-FOFEM.</div>';
